# MASReady – Audit Checklist Integration Prompt for Replit

## Context

You are working inside the `paananiruddh/masready` GitHub repository.
The relevant codebase is at `artifacts/masready/` — this is a React + Wouter + Tailwind + framer-motion SPA that serves as the MASReady marketing/demo site.

The goal of this task is to integrate a new **Environment Audit Checklist** page and tool into the existing marketing site, consistent with its existing design system, routing structure, and component patterns.

---

## What you are adding

A new page at route `/audit-checklist` that:

1. Links to and/or embeds the MASReady Environment Audit Checklist tool (a Perplexity-hosted React app)
2. Is registered in the `Navbar` and `App.tsx` router
3. Follows the existing design system (dark bg, `text-white` headings, `text-muted-foreground` body, `border-white/10` cards, `framer-motion` scroll animations, `container mx-auto px-4`)
4. Includes a clear disclaimer matching the existing trust language in the site

---

## Step 1 — Add the route to `artifacts/masready/src/App.tsx`

Import and register a new page called `AuditChecklist` in the `Design1Router`:

```tsx
import AuditChecklist from "@/pages/audit-checklist";

// Inside Design1Router <Switch>:
<Route path="/audit-checklist" component={AuditChecklist} />
```

---

## Step 2 — Add the nav link to `artifacts/masready/src/components/layout/Navbar.tsx`

Add a new entry to `NAV_LINKS`:

```tsx
{ href: "/audit-checklist", label: "Audit Checklist" },
```

Place it after `{ href: "/trust", label: "Trust Center" }`.

Also add the same link to:
- `artifacts/masready/src/components/layout/Design2Layout.tsx` (if it has its own NAV_LINKS array)
- `artifacts/masready/src/components/layout/Design3Layout.tsx` (if it has its own NAV_LINKS array)

