## Safety constraints (do not violate)

- Do NOT modify any demo data, seed data, constants, or existing page logic
- Do NOT change the existing route structure — only add new routes
- Do NOT add any API calls, backend dependencies, or external data fetching
- Do NOT use localStorage or sessionStorage
- The audit checklist page is a STATIC marketing/landing page — no state management required beyond framer-motion animations
- Keep the disclaimer wording consistent with existing trust language in `trust.tsx`

